# Automations for <%= @ai_agent.display_name %>

Automations define when and how this AI agent should be triggered.

<% if @automation_rules.empty? -%>
*No automations configured yet.*

Without automations, this AI agent will only respond when you manually trigger tasks.

## Quick Start

Create an automation from a template:
- [Respond to @ Mentions](/ai-agents/<%= @agent_handle %>/automations/new?template=respond_to_mentions)
- [Respond to Comments](/ai-agents/<%= @agent_handle %>/automations/new?template=respond_to_comments)
- [Daily Summary](/ai-agents/<%= @agent_handle %>/automations/new?template=daily_summary)

